"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:9.4.3\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">9.4.3</span> 标题：个（饼）（loaf）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：כִּכָּר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kikar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:23\">EXO 29:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:5\">JDG 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:36\">1SA 2:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:3\">1SA 10:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:3\">1CH 16:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:26\">PRO 6:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:21\">JER 37:21</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：צְלִיל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tslil)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:13\">JDG 7:13</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0527_bread_tandir.jpg\" alt=\"一迭扁面包（圆面饼）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">一迭扁面包（圆面饼） (© jeffreyw, CC BY 2.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>“个”是饼的量词。饼一般是扁圆形的，大约有手指张开后的一只手那么大。不过，饼的大小和形状可能有很大的差别。经文提到有三种饼：第一种小饼和今天的面包卷或饼干类似；第二种饼大又圆；第三种饼扁而薄，用来像勺子一样舀食物吃。一般来说，比较富有的人吃小麦做的饼，穷人吃大麦做的饼（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:13\">JDG 7:13</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:7\">JHN 6:7</a> ）。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0527_bread_tandir.jpg\" alt=\"一迭扁面包（圆面饼）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">一迭扁面包（圆面饼） (© jeffreyw, CC BY 2.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>大多数有“饼”一词的语言也会有表示“饼”的量词。在很多经文中，“饼”就表示“一个饼”的意思（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">9.4 饼、面包 (bread)&lt;REALIA:9.4&gt;</a> 中的讨论）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:13\">JDG 7:13</a> ：在这节经文中，这个大麦饼的重要特征是它滚下了山。如果目标语言根据形状来区分饼的种类，那么这里适合采用表示圆饼的词。</p>\n<p>圣饼、陈设饼、供饼：参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.3.5.1 供饼 (consecrated bread, bread of the presence, showbread)&lt;REALIA:4.3.5.1&gt;</a> 。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
